Module com.hack23.cia.web

Package com.hack23.cia.web.impl.ui.application.views.common.menufactory.impl

package com.hack23.cia.web.impl.ui.application.views.common.menufactory.impl
This package provides classes and interfaces for creating and managing menu items within the Citizen Intelligence Agency web application. Key classes and interfaces: - AbstractMenuItemFactoryImpl: Base class for creating menu items. - ApplicationMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the ApplicationMenuItemFactory interface. - BallotMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the BallotMenuItemFactory interface. - CommitteeMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the CommitteeMenuItemFactory interface. - CommitteeRankingMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the CommitteeRankingMenuItemFactory interface. - CountryMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the CountryMenuItemFactory interface. - DocumentMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the DocumentMenuItemFactory interface. - GovernmentBodyMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the GovernmentBodyMenuItemFactory interface. - GovernmentBodyRankingMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the GovernmentBodyRankingMenuItemFactory interface. - MinistryMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the MinistryMenuItemFactory interface. - MinistryRankingMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the MinistryRankingMenuItemFactory interface. - ParliamentMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the ParliamentMenuItemFactory interface. - PartyMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the PartyMenuItemFactory interface. - PartyRankingMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the PartyRankingMenuItemFactory interface. - PoliticianMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the PoliticianMenuItemFactory interface. - PoliticianRankingMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the PoliticianRankingMenuItemFactory interface. - UserHomeMenuItemFactoryImpl: Implementation of the UserHomeMenuItemFactory interface. Dependencies and relationships: - Depends on com.hack23.cia.web.impl.ui.application.util for UserContextUtil. - Depends on com.hack23.cia.web.impl.ui.application.views.common.pagelinks.api for PageModeMenuCommand. - Depends on com.hack23.cia.web.impl.ui.application.views.common.viewnames for various view names and page modes. - Depends on com.jarektoro.responsivelayout for responsive layout classes. - Depends on com.vaadin for Vaadin framework classes and interfaces. - Depends on org.springframework for Spring framework classes and interfaces.
